-2", "frontend-0", "cartservice-0", "recommendationservice-1", "shippingservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["frontend-2", "checkoutservice-0", "currencyservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["paymentservice-2", "cartservice-1", "currencyservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["productcatalogservice-0", "checkoutservice-2", "emailservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["shippingservice-2", "frontend-1", "emailservice-0", "currencyservice-2", "adservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["paymentservice-0", "cartservice-2", "adservice-2", "recommendationservice-0", "redis-cart-0", "shippingservice-1"]}, "available_metric_names": ["client_error_ratio", "error_ratio", "pod_cpu_usage", "request", "response", "rrt_max", "server_error_ratio"], "log_analysis_findings": "基于对异常时间段内日志数据的分析，我已经完成了初始扫描阶段。以下是分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"context canceled\", \"rpc error\", \"code = Canceled\", \"failed to get product recommendations\", \"could not retrieve currencies\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"RPC调用被取消，多个frontend实例报告无法获取产品推荐信息，表明productcatalogservice可能响应超时或不可用\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to get product recommendations: rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice\", \n      \"reason\": \"RPC调用被取消，frontend服务无法获取货币信息，表明currencyservice可能响应超时或不可用\",\n      \"evidence\": \"could not retrieve currencies: rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"作为调用方，所有错误日志都来自frontend服务，但问题可能源于其依赖的下游服务\",\n      \"evidence\": \"所有日志均来自frontend服务的3个实例（frontend-0、frontend-1、frontend-2）\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**关键发现**：\n1. **错误模式一致**：所有错误都是RPC调用被取消（context canceled），表明存在超时或服务不可用问题\n2. **影响范围广泛**：涉及frontend服务的所有3个实例，分布在3个不同节点上\n3. **主要影响功能**：产品推荐获取和货币信息检索功能\n4. **时间分布**：错误集中在09:11-09:15期间，之后有零星错误\n\n**建议下一步**：需要进一步分析productcatalogservice和currencyservice的监控指标和日志，以确定是这些服务本身的问题还是网络连接问题。", "trace_analysis_findings": "基于对异常时间段 2025-06-08T09:10:31Z 至 2025-06-08T09:32:31Z 的链路追踪数据分析，我发现了显著的异常模式。以下是初步扫描结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"frontend->recommendationservice\",\n    \"recommendationservice->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->emailservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->paymentservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"recommendationservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"推荐服务延迟异常严重：正常平均耗时约120-140ms，异常时段飙升至58,000ms+，延迟倍数高达470倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\", \n      \"evidence\": \"产品目录服务延迟增加：从recommendationservice调用ListProducts时，延迟从3s增加到13.8s，延迟倍数4.6倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"结账服务下游依赖延迟：EmailService延迟从20s增加到89s，ShippingService从12.5s增加到83.4s，PaymentService从12.8s增加到66s\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"前端服务大量HTTP 500错误和context canceled错误，表明下游服务异常导致请求失败\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**关键发现**：\n1. **推荐服务(recommendationservice)是主要瓶颈**：延迟异常严重，是调用链中最下游的异常服务\n2. **错误传播路径**：recommendationservice → productcatalogservice → 整个调用链\n3. **连锁反应**：推荐服务异常导致前端大量context canceled和HTTP 500错误\n4. **结账流程受影响**：虽然checkoutservice本身延迟增加，但主要是下游依赖服务异常导致\n\n需要进一步分析recommendationservice的具体问题，可能是资源不足、数据库连接问题或代码逻辑异常。", "metric_analysis_findings": "根据提供的指标数据和分析结果，以下是初步扫描阶段发现的显著异常调用链和潜在问题：\n\n### 检测到的异常指标\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"client_error_ratio\",\n    \"server_error_ratio\",\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\",\n    \"rrt_max\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"显著增加的error_ratio和client_error_ratio，同时pod_cpu_usage异常下降\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio从0.0增加到42.86，client_error_ratio从0.0增加到42.86，pod_cpu_usage从0.06下降到0.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"显著增加的error_ratio和server_error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio从0.0增加到15.13，server_error_ratio从0.0增加到15.13\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"显著增加的error_ratio和server_error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio从0.0增加到8.95，server_error_ratio从0.0增加到8.95\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"显著增加的error_ratio和server_error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio从0.0增加到14.4，server_error_ratio从0.0增加到14.4\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"显著增加的error_ratio和client_error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio从0.0增加到62.5，client_error_ratio从0.0增加到62.5\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"显著增加的error_ratio和client_error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio从0.0增加到60.0，client_error_ratio从0.0增加到60.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"显著增加的error_ratio和client_error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio从0.0增加到62.5，client_error_ratio从0.0增加到62.5\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"recommendationservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"显著增加的rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max从21802.0增加到9006.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"显著增加的rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max从265051.0增加到60001762.0\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 分析要点\n1. **服务错误率异常**：\n   - `productcatalogservice`、`frontend`和`shippingservice`的多个Pod表现出显著的`error_ratio`和`client_error_ratio`或`server_error_ratio`增加。\n   - 这表明这些服务在处理请求时可能遇到了问题，例如依赖服务不可用或内部逻辑错误。\n\n2. **CPU使用率异常**：\n   - `productcatalogservice-0`的`pod_cpu_usage`显著下降，可能与错误率增加相关（例如服务崩溃或重启）。\n\n3. **响应时间异常**：\n   - `recommendationservice-0`和`frontend-2`的`rrt_max`显著增加，表明这些服务的响应时间出现了极端峰值，可能是性能瓶颈或资源争用导致的。\n\n### 下一步建议\n- 深入分析`productcatalogservice-0`的日志，确认是否因CPU使用率异常导致服务崩溃。\n- 检查`frontend`和`shippingservice`的依赖服务（如数据库或下游服务）是否正常。\n- 分析`recommendationservice-0`和`frontend-2`的资源使用情况，确认是否存在资源不足或配置问题。"}
